{"word":"G573 - ἁπλοῦς - haploûs - hap-looce' - Single","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἁπλοῦς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">haploûs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hap-looce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Single</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தெளிவு - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"simple, single, whole, sound"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably from <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a particle of union) and the base of <a href=\"#/G4120 - πλέκω - plékō - plek'-o/4120\">G4120</a>; properly <i>folded together</i>, that is, <i>single</i> (figuratively <i>clear</i>): - single.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G572/572\">G572</a>, <a href=\"#/G573/573\">G573</a>"}]}